headline: DuPont Water Technologies Featured in Avoided-Emissions Use Case by World Business Council for Sustainable Development
summary: DuPont Water Solutions, using the World Business Council for Sustainable Development (WBCSD) Avoided Emissions Guidance, has shared an early example of how to use the framework to measure the impact of carbon-avoiding solutions in the water sector.
